TestNG
-------------
Parameterization
----------------
1) XML File  ---> Parallel testing
2) @DataProvider

Parameterization using XML File
-----------------
1) create test case
2) Execute test case using xml file
3) Pass browser name as a parametr from xml file to test case
4) Execute test on multiple browsers sequencially(serial execution).
5) Execute test on multiple browsers parallely(parallel execution).

